WEBVTT

00:16.410 --> 00:20.910
ظآزDuring the dark nightظآز

00:21.080 --> 00:23.710
ظآزA guiding lightظآز

00:24.210 --> 00:25.980
ظآزJust like youظآز

00:26.410 --> 00:30.680
ظآزMakes life turn brightظآز

00:31.280 --> 00:36.110
ظآزBreaking free from darknessظآز

00:36.380 --> 00:39.850
ظآزYou gave me strengthظآز

00:40.180 --> 00:42.710
ظآزRunning for truthظآز

00:42.780 --> 00:46.810
ظآزI find my pathظآز

00:47.580 --> 00:51.550
ظآزDrawing on the hopeظآز

00:52.180 --> 00:55.550
ظآزThat you render meظآز

00:56.080 --> 00:58.950
ظآزIn this long journeyظآز

00:59.210 --> 01:02.610
ظآزI run on lightlyظآز

01:20.150 --> 01:23.950
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:24.450 --> 01:25.050
It's fine.

01:25.480 --> 01:26.880
Even though you're not as pretty as her,

01:26.880 --> 01:27.680
I like it when you pretend

01:27.710 --> 01:28.950
as if you were a decent girl.

01:29.210 --> 01:30.080
You have no idea what she was like...

01:30.080 --> 01:30.880
Shut up.

01:31.450 --> 01:32.250
I'm saying it anyway.

01:32.580 --> 01:34.009
You have no idea
what she was like, do you?

01:34.410 --> 01:35.509
Especially when she was drunk.

01:36.110 --> 01:37.479
She would do everything I told her to.

01:37.479 --> 01:38.009
Let go of me!

01:41.910 --> 01:42.580
She's got a knife!

02:03.780 --> 02:04.650
I've called the police.

02:11.710 --> 02:13.010
Hei, let's go.

02:17.410 --> 02:19.579
Just you wait.

02:19.579 --> 02:23.450
ظآزPerhapsظآز

02:24.110 --> 02:29.650
ظآزWe were afraid of losingظآز

02:30.810 --> 02:36.310
ظآزThat's why we were hesitantظآز

02:36.310 --> 02:37.310
Are you alright?

02:37.350 --> 02:42.780
ظآزBut you lingerظآز

02:56.780 --> 03:01.580
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

03:02.450 --> 03:03.950
ظآزIs your nameظآز

03:03.980 --> 03:04.510
Don't be afraid.

03:06.110 --> 03:06.810
I'm here with you.

03:06.850 --> 03:11.810
ظآزThe only stubbornness in my heartظآز

03:12.510 --> 03:15.910
ظآزFortunately, I'm not sensible enoughظآز

03:16.510 --> 03:19.650
ظآزCourage wasn't late tooظآز

03:20.450 --> 03:26.180
ظآزOnly then does time
not betray our acquaintanceظآز

03:35.180 --> 03:40.050
[Episode 8]
[You Have Me]

03:50.810 --> 03:52.010
Dad, Mom. Have some tea.

03:52.910 --> 03:55.710
[Fang Yanqiu: Where are you?]

04:04.980 --> 04:06.510
[Fang Yanqiu: Where are you?]

04:06.510 --> 04:09.880
[Mr. Sun calling]

04:10.810 --> 04:11.250
Hello?

04:11.550 --> 04:12.750
Is this Ming Sheng's father?

04:13.810 --> 04:15.180
Something happened to Ming Sheng
at school.

04:30.010 --> 04:30.880
This is embarrassing.

04:37.810 --> 04:38.510
Ms. Li.

04:39.280 --> 04:41.610
Mr. Sun, sorry for causing you trouble.

04:42.610 --> 04:43.610
Don't do this.

04:43.650 --> 04:44.610
Let me introduce.

04:44.810 --> 04:46.650
This is Qiao Qingyu's mother.

04:48.880 --> 04:49.650
Mr. Ming, you're here.

04:49.680 --> 04:50.980
Hello, Mr. Sun. Hello, Dean.

04:54.880 --> 04:55.909
What's the matter?
Do you know each other?

04:59.050 --> 04:59.810
No.

05:00.450 --> 05:02.210
Are you Qiao Qingyu's mother?

05:02.950 --> 05:04.010
I'm Ming Sheng's father.

05:04.250 --> 05:04.950
Hello.

05:07.350 --> 05:08.450
I believe

05:09.010 --> 05:11.450
Mr. Sun has explained
what happened to you two.

05:12.680 --> 05:13.780
Ms. Li.

05:14.210 --> 05:15.780
What happened at the school gate

05:16.050 --> 05:17.110
is still under investigation.

05:17.680 --> 05:20.110
The hooligans
have been sent to the police station.

05:20.110 --> 05:21.380
It has left a negative impact.

05:21.850 --> 05:24.480
Does Qiao Qingyu have a sister?

05:24.810 --> 05:26.780
We heard about it too.

05:27.280 --> 05:29.350
We sympathize
with what happened to your family,

05:30.280 --> 05:32.409
but today's incident
has had a negative impact.

05:33.510 --> 05:34.210
So

05:34.450 --> 05:36.909
please ensure Qingyu is disciplined.

05:37.110 --> 05:39.710
Qingyu should stay home
and reflect for two days.

05:40.510 --> 05:42.810
Sir, let me
apologize to you on her behalf.

05:42.980 --> 05:44.510
She's still young and needs guidance.

05:44.810 --> 05:46.409
I failed to discipline her.

05:46.650 --> 05:47.780
I know she's wrong.

05:47.909 --> 05:49.010
Let me apologize to you,

05:49.350 --> 05:51.450
the teachers and everyone on her behalf.

05:52.250 --> 05:54.150
But she's a diligent student
with a passion for learning.

05:54.180 --> 05:55.480
You need to make sure
she continues her education.

05:55.810 --> 05:57.350
Could you give her another chance?

06:02.550 --> 06:04.380
My injury has nothing to do
with Qiao Qingyu.

06:05.480 --> 06:07.210
I asked her for the cutter

06:07.250 --> 06:08.510
and accidentally cut my hand.

06:08.910 --> 06:10.510
This whole thing
is just a misunderstanding.

06:10.680 --> 06:11.510
Ming Sheng.

06:11.910 --> 06:13.380
Don't talk nonsense.

06:13.480 --> 06:15.280
That's not what the other students said.

06:15.410 --> 06:16.980
Sir, it's not nonsense.

06:17.750 --> 06:19.010
And I'm the one involved.

06:19.110 --> 06:20.180
I'm sure I'm the one

06:20.380 --> 06:21.710
who knows best what happened.

06:22.080 --> 06:22.380
You...

06:22.410 --> 06:25.710
Sir, those troublemaking hooligans

06:26.010 --> 06:27.350
have been detained by the police

06:27.610 --> 06:28.810
for causing trouble.

06:29.150 --> 06:31.680
The ringleader
will be locked up for a while.

06:31.880 --> 06:33.210
These people have criminal records

06:33.310 --> 06:34.810
and often harass girls.

06:35.580 --> 06:38.110
By the way,
Qiao Qingyu is also a victim.

06:38.750 --> 06:39.580
So,

06:40.110 --> 06:41.710
we can't punish the victim
for the mistakes

06:41.710 --> 06:42.909
made by a few hooligans.

06:42.909 --> 06:44.210
If this becomes public,

06:44.280 --> 06:46.010
others will ridicule us

06:46.110 --> 06:48.250
for confusing right and wrong.

06:48.580 --> 06:48.980
Sir.

06:50.150 --> 06:52.480
Since Ming Sheng's injury
and the rioting

06:52.580 --> 06:54.010
have nothing to do with Qiao Qingyu,

06:54.310 --> 06:55.050
I think

06:55.080 --> 06:56.810
that the school has no reason
to punish her.

06:58.280 --> 06:59.080
I did hear

06:59.810 --> 07:01.810
some rumors

07:02.080 --> 07:03.510
about Qiao Qingyu's sister.

07:04.080 --> 07:05.380
As a healthcare worker,

07:06.080 --> 07:07.180
I implore the school

07:07.480 --> 07:09.580
to address this critical knowledge gap.

07:10.110 --> 07:12.250
This will ensure students
are well-informed

07:12.280 --> 07:13.710
and avoid unnecessary anxiety.

07:14.610 --> 07:15.010
Yes.

07:17.780 --> 07:18.910
Alright, Ms. Li.

07:18.950 --> 07:19.850
Let's keep in touch.

07:22.380 --> 07:23.980
Qingyu,

07:23.980 --> 07:25.050
you need to learn from this.

07:25.550 --> 07:26.780
Next time,

07:26.780 --> 07:27.450
ask your teachers

07:27.480 --> 07:28.980
and parents for help immediately.

07:29.510 --> 07:31.210
Don't rush ahead recklessly.

07:31.950 --> 07:33.210
You're still young.

07:33.680 --> 07:35.150
It's our responsibility
as adults to protect you.

07:35.310 --> 07:35.950
Got it?

07:36.880 --> 07:38.280
Is the school not going to punish me?

07:38.580 --> 07:39.850
Ming Sheng has explained

07:40.110 --> 07:41.350
that his injury is just an accident.

07:41.980 --> 07:43.450
The school has no reason to punish you.

07:48.380 --> 07:49.510
Mr. Sun, we got to go.

07:49.550 --> 07:50.610
Sure, take care.

07:51.550 --> 07:53.780
Ms. Li, don't scold her
when you get home.

07:57.350 --> 07:58.210
Go with your mom now.

08:04.380 --> 08:05.250
You're just causing me embarrassment.

08:25.350 --> 08:26.410
Why did you

08:27.050 --> 08:28.380
help Qiao Qingyu at school today?

08:28.880 --> 08:30.080
Didn't you want to help her?

08:31.050 --> 08:32.309
Since she's your friend,

08:32.679 --> 08:34.750
I don't think
she will do anything wrong.

08:36.510 --> 08:37.950
Be careful not to get the wound wet.

08:39.309 --> 08:40.650
Rest for the next few days.

08:40.679 --> 08:41.650
Stay at my place

08:41.850 --> 08:42.650
so that I can take care of you.

08:46.810 --> 08:49.410
[Fang Yanqiu]

08:57.880 --> 08:59.010
Why didn't you pick up the phone?

08:59.580 --> 09:00.610
Am I bothering you?

09:00.610 --> 09:03.280
No, it's nothing important.

09:03.310 --> 09:04.380
I'll reply to them later.

09:06.380 --> 09:07.480
What do you want to eat tonight?

09:07.510 --> 09:08.210
I'll make it for you.

09:10.380 --> 09:11.050
Anything will do.

09:28.810 --> 09:29.310
Qingyu.

09:30.150 --> 09:33.350
Do you think Mom is angry with you,
like she's "chopping you up"

09:33.350 --> 09:36.250
as if you were dumpling filling?

09:38.380 --> 09:40.010
Qingyu, tell me.

09:40.450 --> 09:42.450
Were you really planning to stab

09:42.450 --> 09:43.510
that hooligan?

09:45.110 --> 09:46.580
Qingyu, I'm so impressed.

09:46.610 --> 09:49.050
You're an admirable girl.

09:50.180 --> 09:53.280
I heard that you also
accidentally injured Ming Sheng.

09:53.710 --> 09:55.850
He's so tough. I can't believe
he didn't settle a score with you.

09:56.380 --> 09:57.880
Is something wrong with him?

10:13.880 --> 10:14.780
Don't be afraid.

10:15.910 --> 10:17.210
I'm here with you.

10:44.550 --> 10:45.110
Ming Sheng.

10:46.250 --> 10:46.880
Ming Sheng.

10:47.480 --> 10:48.150
The meal's ready.

11:01.380 --> 11:01.550
Hello?

11:02.280 --> 11:04.280
Hello? Is this Dr. Ming?

11:04.610 --> 11:05.410
He's cooking.

11:05.680 --> 11:07.380
Oh, you're Ming Sheng.

11:08.050 --> 11:09.580
I'm Madam Zhang
from the neighborhood committee.

11:09.710 --> 11:11.580
Your dad said
he has some sheet music at home

11:11.610 --> 11:13.610
that he wants to donate
to the community center.

11:13.710 --> 11:15.580
I want to ask him
if he has packed them up yet.

11:15.610 --> 11:16.250
Sheet music?

11:32.010 --> 11:32.680
What's that supposed to mean?

11:35.810 --> 11:36.510
Your mother said

11:36.510 --> 11:38.010
she didn't want them anymore

11:38.050 --> 11:38.980
and asked me to deal with them.

11:40.780 --> 11:41.680
I see.

11:42.310 --> 11:43.350
You want to make room.

11:44.450 --> 11:45.150
Don't worry.

11:45.480 --> 11:47.250
My mom and I won't get in your way.

11:48.910 --> 11:49.450
Ming Sheng.

11:54.710 --> 11:55.050
Ming Sheng.

11:56.780 --> 11:57.310
Ming Sheng!

12:58.650 --> 13:00.710
Why are you up so late at night?

13:01.880 --> 13:03.210
We chose a bad name for our daughter.

13:03.550 --> 13:04.550
Huh?

13:05.080 --> 13:06.510
We need to change Qing's name.

13:08.380 --> 13:09.180
What do you mean?

13:11.180 --> 13:12.180
I asked around.

13:13.710 --> 13:15.380
Qiao Beiyu, Qiao Qingyu.

13:16.410 --> 13:18.010
It's bad luck for a girl to be named Yu.

13:18.680 --> 13:19.350
We can't keep them.

13:20.410 --> 13:21.410
Bei's gone.

13:23.110 --> 13:23.980
I'm scared Qing...

13:24.250 --> 13:25.450
Nonsense.

13:26.210 --> 13:28.280
Stop looking for trouble.

13:28.610 --> 13:30.850
Do you think you can

13:30.850 --> 13:32.010
change names as you please?

13:32.880 --> 13:33.950
Go to bed.

13:52.410 --> 13:55.010
Something happened to Ming Sheng
at school yesterday.

13:55.310 --> 13:56.550
I couldn't get away.

13:56.950 --> 13:57.580
I'm so sorry.

13:58.910 --> 14:00.680
Didn't you already explain
on the phone yesterday?

14:00.780 --> 14:01.450
I understand.

14:02.610 --> 14:04.180
Your son is more important, of course.

14:04.310 --> 14:05.310
That's not what I meant.

14:13.310 --> 14:14.150
Let me

14:14.780 --> 14:16.180
treat your parents to dinner tonight.

14:18.650 --> 14:19.650
They've gone home.

14:19.880 --> 14:20.810
Next time.

14:28.080 --> 14:28.710
Yanqiu.

14:30.780 --> 14:30.950
I...

14:30.950 --> 14:31.410
Yanqiu.

14:32.910 --> 14:33.780
The nursing department
is asking for you.

14:34.110 --> 14:34.980
Coming.

14:42.880 --> 14:44.150
Before the teacher comes,

14:44.180 --> 14:46.580
let's solve these questions in advance.

14:47.810 --> 14:50.380
The thought of those scumbags
from No.1 High School acting smug

14:50.380 --> 14:51.450
gets under my skin.

14:52.080 --> 14:53.050
Were it not for Ming Sheng's absence,

14:53.050 --> 14:54.110
would we have lost to them?

14:54.910 --> 14:56.010
Enough. We have problems too.

14:56.050 --> 14:56.650
What?

15:01.050 --> 15:02.380
Look at his hand.

15:02.880 --> 15:03.950
It looks serious.

15:04.050 --> 15:05.350
Will there be any side effects?

15:08.310 --> 15:09.110
Qiao Qingyu.

15:09.550 --> 15:10.610
If it weren't for you,

15:10.650 --> 15:11.880
Ming Sheng
wouldn't have injured his hand.

15:11.880 --> 15:13.010
And we wouldn't have lost the game.

15:13.210 --> 15:14.610
You must apologize to Ming Sheng!

15:23.480 --> 15:24.310
Speak!

15:28.010 --> 15:28.810
Is it difficult to apologize?

15:30.050 --> 15:31.510
Or do you think you did nothing wrong?

15:38.680 --> 15:39.780
Just apologize.

15:40.210 --> 15:41.850
It's indeed your fault.

15:43.010 --> 15:44.010
Have you had enough?

15:45.280 --> 15:46.180
It's between Qiao Qingyu and me,

15:46.210 --> 15:47.680
whether she apologizes or not.

15:47.910 --> 15:49.450
This is none of your business.

15:51.050 --> 15:52.050
Be quiet.

15:52.080 --> 15:53.550
Don't you know
it's the self-study period right now?

15:53.680 --> 15:54.310
Alright.

16:26.180 --> 16:27.180
Are you okay?

16:27.280 --> 16:28.450
Did you see who did that?

16:28.650 --> 16:29.450
How immoral.

16:30.410 --> 16:31.510
I didn't see,

16:31.810 --> 16:32.510
but I know who did it.

16:36.610 --> 16:38.880
Did you see how pathetic she looked?

16:39.180 --> 16:41.110
I wanted to take a picture.

16:41.910 --> 16:43.810
Do you think she knew it was us?

16:45.380 --> 16:46.480
What if she tells the teachers?

16:46.810 --> 16:47.880
Does she have any proof?

17:13.079 --> 17:14.079
Qingyu, are you okay?

17:14.250 --> 17:15.880
I hope they didn't give you
any more trouble.

17:16.710 --> 17:17.450
No.

17:18.010 --> 17:20.480
The Dean of Discipline
has reprimanded them.

17:20.680 --> 17:21.950
They also apologized to me.

17:23.849 --> 17:24.680
Thank you.

17:26.480 --> 17:27.349
Don't mention it.

17:37.610 --> 17:38.410
Here.

17:39.880 --> 17:40.650
This is for you.

17:44.010 --> 17:47.150
You were watching me
dance that day, right?

18:08.780 --> 18:12.180
ظآزUnder the sunlightظآز

18:12.210 --> 18:16.010
ظآزBirds take a flyظآز

18:16.010 --> 18:20.610
ظآزRaise me up, hold me highظآز

18:20.650 --> 18:23.950
ظآزOnly youظآز

18:24.510 --> 18:28.980
ظآزDuring the dark nightظآز

18:29.010 --> 18:32.480
ظآزA guiding lightظآز

18:32.480 --> 18:34.080
ظآزJust like youظآز

18:34.110 --> 18:37.080
ظآزMakes life turn brightظآز

18:37.080 --> 18:38.550
Have you learned this before?

18:39.750 --> 18:41.580
Someone taught me a little before.

18:41.610 --> 18:43.210
ظآزBreaking free from darknessظآز

18:43.250 --> 18:44.150
This should go outward.

18:44.480 --> 18:46.210
Yes, look this way.

18:46.710 --> 18:48.950
Extend your fingers outward.

18:48.950 --> 18:50.010
ظآزRunning for truthظآز

18:50.050 --> 18:51.410
Good. Continue.

18:51.410 --> 18:56.450
ظآزI find my pathظآز

18:56.450 --> 19:00.650
ظآزDrawing on the hopeظآز

19:00.680 --> 19:04.280
ظآزThat you render meظآز

19:04.280 --> 19:07.610
ظآزIn this long journeyظآز

19:08.250 --> 19:08.950
Here, Qing.

19:09.880 --> 19:11.080
Raise your arm.

19:12.650 --> 19:14.010
Raise it.

19:23.250 --> 19:25.250
Qing is amazing!

19:28.680 --> 19:30.480
Qing.

19:31.580 --> 19:32.380
Qingyu.

19:34.010 --> 19:34.750
Qingyu?

19:38.950 --> 19:39.750
What did you say?

19:40.250 --> 19:41.180
I just asked you

19:41.210 --> 19:42.850
if you wanted to join our dance club.

19:44.950 --> 19:46.250
I'll think about it.

19:46.280 --> 19:47.410
ظآزUnder the sunlightظآز

19:47.450 --> 19:48.850
Sure, no problem.

19:48.850 --> 19:51.380
ظآزBirds take a flyظآز

19:51.410 --> 19:52.210
On the 28th,

19:52.250 --> 19:53.980
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]
National Meteorological Center issued

19:54.010 --> 19:55.750
the first orange cold wave warning.

19:56.010 --> 19:57.250
Since the beginning of winter this year,

19:57.380 --> 19:59.710
the strongest cold air
has been affecting most of the country,

19:59.910 --> 20:01.980
moving from west to east
and north to south.

20:02.710 --> 20:03.950
Hello? Qiao's Noodle House.

20:04.610 --> 20:05.310
Go ahead.

20:06.050 --> 20:07.980
Chaoyang Village.

20:09.850 --> 20:12.880
Block 13, 806.

20:12.880 --> 20:14.810
A serving of fried noodles,
non-spicy, right?

20:15.680 --> 20:16.780
Alright. It will be delivered soon.

20:17.110 --> 20:19.150
Qiao Huan, let me deliver this order.

20:19.180 --> 20:20.380
Aren't you going to the library?

20:20.950 --> 20:21.580
It's on my way there.

20:22.380 --> 20:22.750
Sure.

20:47.680 --> 20:48.710
Your takeout has arrived.

20:50.180 --> 20:52.080
Your order
from Qiao's Noodle House is here.

21:00.580 --> 21:02.480
We have some new promotions.

21:02.480 --> 21:03.510
Would you like to hear about them?

21:03.810 --> 21:04.410
No, thanks.

21:04.710 --> 21:06.410
You order from us often.

21:06.450 --> 21:07.180
The promotions are perfect for you.

21:07.310 --> 21:08.310
I've told you I'm good.

21:08.310 --> 21:09.550
I'll be quick.

21:13.010 --> 21:13.680
Ouch.

21:14.250 --> 21:15.110
What are you doing?

21:31.450 --> 21:33.680
I didn't expect
to find your place like this

21:33.680 --> 21:34.780
while you always seem
so together at school.

21:34.810 --> 21:36.410
I really want those classmates
to see you like this.

21:36.750 --> 21:38.110
I can't believe you'd say that.

21:38.750 --> 21:39.680
If it weren't for you,

21:39.710 --> 21:41.150
would I be in such a mess,

21:41.280 --> 21:42.080
huh?

21:47.180 --> 21:47.880
Sorry.

21:53.680 --> 21:54.380
That is unexpected.

21:59.750 --> 22:01.180
Didn't you act

22:02.110 --> 22:04.110
so unyielding at school yesterday?

22:05.310 --> 22:06.710
I was too impulsive.

22:07.080 --> 22:08.750
I'd be in a lot of trouble
if it weren't for you.

22:13.110 --> 22:14.680
I'm sorry for injuring you.

22:19.180 --> 22:20.710
Do you think
an apology will fix everything?

22:21.480 --> 22:22.510
What else do you want?

22:25.050 --> 22:26.180
I want you to atone for your sins.

23:53.850 --> 23:54.510
What are you doing?

23:55.310 --> 23:56.110
Who told you to look through this?

23:56.750 --> 23:57.180
Huh?

23:58.410 --> 23:59.750
I wanted to help you sort it out.

23:59.750 --> 24:00.250
I didn't mean it.

24:00.280 --> 24:01.580
You still can't just
look through my things.

24:03.810 --> 24:05.210
We're even now.

24:05.350 --> 24:05.880
Leave.

24:07.950 --> 24:08.750
Leave!

24:41.050 --> 24:41.850
Qiao Qingyu.

24:43.450 --> 24:43.980
Morning.

24:58.610 --> 24:59.480
Don't wander around.

25:13.610 --> 25:14.150
Hey.

25:16.480 --> 25:18.350
Qiao Qingyu, what a coincidence.

25:26.610 --> 25:27.310
What do you want?

25:28.750 --> 25:30.210
Do you still want your letter?

25:30.480 --> 25:31.350
What letter?

25:33.050 --> 25:35.280
A letter
from your dear former classmate,

25:35.650 --> 25:37.580
Niao Mingkai*
[Similar form with Ma, means silly].

25:38.010 --> 25:39.110
I kept forgetting to bring it to you.

25:39.810 --> 25:41.410
Meet me at the tree after school.

25:41.950 --> 25:42.980
If you don't come,

25:43.810 --> 25:44.950
I'll assume you don't want it anymore.

25:45.250 --> 25:45.980
I'll take care of it myself.

25:46.080 --> 25:46.810
It's up to you.

25:46.850 --> 25:47.350
Sheng.

25:47.880 --> 25:49.380
Faster. Free time awaits us
after this run.

25:49.450 --> 25:50.110
Let's go.

25:51.410 --> 25:52.480
See you.

26:13.280 --> 26:14.080
Come up.

26:18.010 --> 26:18.880
Do you still want the letter?

26:25.510 --> 26:26.310
Where's the letter?

26:28.410 --> 26:29.710
Close your eyes.

26:30.480 --> 26:31.150
Why?

26:31.880 --> 26:33.180
Don't worry about it.
Just do as I say.

26:36.210 --> 26:36.880
And then what?

26:39.280 --> 26:41.780
Do you hear a sound?

26:53.250 --> 26:55.810
Actually, the tree can talk.

26:56.950 --> 26:58.150
It's saying...

27:04.480 --> 27:05.350
Sorry.

27:10.180 --> 27:11.180
You're fooling with me.

27:11.280 --> 27:12.350
I'm not.

27:15.650 --> 27:17.310
I shouldn't have
lost my temper with you yesterday.

27:18.580 --> 27:19.380
Sorry.

27:24.050 --> 27:25.610
Those records and albums

27:25.610 --> 27:26.710
are actually my mom's.

27:27.610 --> 27:28.910
This place

27:29.950 --> 27:31.910
was also my secret base with my mom.

27:33.750 --> 27:35.010
Do you want to hear my story?

27:45.710 --> 27:46.710
My parents divorced

27:48.210 --> 27:49.610
when I was very young.

27:51.480 --> 27:52.780
I was raised by my grandfather.

27:54.080 --> 27:55.380
The summer
of the senior high school entrance exam,

27:57.010 --> 27:58.080
my grandfather passed away.

28:00.410 --> 28:01.280
From then on,

28:02.880 --> 28:04.150
I became a burden.

28:06.210 --> 28:07.580
That's why I always thought

28:09.450 --> 28:10.950
my birth was a mistake.

28:14.310 --> 28:15.350
So Qiao Qingyu,

28:16.180 --> 28:17.450
you're not the only one with weaknesses.

28:23.250 --> 28:24.910
Why are you telling me all this?

28:26.950 --> 28:28.110
I just want to.

28:33.850 --> 28:34.510
Ming Sheng.

28:34.810 --> 28:35.310
Hmm?

28:38.880 --> 28:40.650
You don't seem as annoying as you look.

29:13.910 --> 29:14.480
I've arrived.

29:17.180 --> 29:17.650
Oh.

29:18.650 --> 29:19.250
Me too.

29:20.310 --> 29:21.610
I'll go upstairs, then.

29:21.710 --> 29:22.210
Hmm.

29:24.080 --> 29:24.880
Qiao Qingyu.

29:32.710 --> 29:33.510
Your letter.

29:34.450 --> 29:35.950
I finally get to give this to you.

29:36.980 --> 29:38.950
[To Qiao Qingyu. From Ma Mingkai]

29:39.880 --> 29:41.450
Are you going to write him back?

29:44.210 --> 29:45.080
Don't get me wrong.

29:45.850 --> 29:47.550
I'm just thinking that the final exam is
around the corner.

29:48.180 --> 29:49.310
I'm afraid
that it will affect your studies.

29:51.380 --> 29:52.710
Well, I'll go now.

29:56.510 --> 29:57.810
I won't write him back.

30:26.450 --> 30:27.250
Qingyu.

30:27.510 --> 30:28.910
Mom, why didn't you knock?

30:29.610 --> 30:31.310
I forgot.

30:31.610 --> 30:32.950
Don't go to school tomorrow morning.

30:32.950 --> 30:33.980
I asked for leave for you.

30:34.810 --> 30:36.080
Go out with me to do some errands.

30:36.080 --> 30:36.780
What is it?

30:37.210 --> 30:38.450
You'll find out later.

30:49.110 --> 30:53.350
[Huanzhou Bus Station]

30:54.910 --> 30:55.580
Hurry.

30:55.750 --> 30:56.780
Where are we going?

30:58.010 --> 30:59.310
We're going back
to our hometown to change your name.

30:59.710 --> 31:01.010
Why do we need to do that?

31:01.480 --> 31:02.380
They said

31:02.410 --> 31:03.880
Qingyu and Beiyu are unlucky names.

31:03.880 --> 31:04.780
We got to change them.

31:05.080 --> 31:06.350
I don't want you
to end up like your sister.

31:06.580 --> 31:07.250
After you change it,

31:07.250 --> 31:08.410
we won't have any more problems.

31:08.410 --> 31:09.080
I'm not going.

31:09.080 --> 31:09.480
Good girl.

31:09.510 --> 31:10.410
I don't want to change my name.

31:10.450 --> 31:11.810
This is my decision, and that's final.

31:11.810 --> 31:13.310
No. I don't want to.

31:13.310 --> 31:14.180
Be a good girl.

31:14.210 --> 31:15.510
I don't want to go!

31:15.850 --> 31:16.650
Hey.

31:16.650 --> 31:18.350
Calm down.

31:18.410 --> 31:19.280
This is my daughter. What are you doing?

31:19.280 --> 31:19.710
She's my daughter.

31:19.710 --> 31:21.110
Let go.

31:21.110 --> 31:21.480
This is my daughter.

31:21.510 --> 31:22.450
Let go.

31:22.480 --> 31:23.110
What are you doing?

31:23.110 --> 31:23.910
Calm down.

31:23.910 --> 31:26.110
She wouldn't stop grabbing the girl.

31:26.310 --> 31:28.450
I don't think the girl
wants to go with her.

31:28.680 --> 31:29.850
I'm Li Fanghao.

31:29.950 --> 31:31.310
Her name is Qiao Qingyu.

31:31.310 --> 31:32.050
She's my daughter.

31:32.080 --> 31:33.380
I'm taking her back to our hometown.

31:33.610 --> 31:35.310
Miss, is this your mother?

31:37.050 --> 31:38.450
She's paying you no attention.

31:38.450 --> 31:39.350
She's ignoring you.

31:39.380 --> 31:40.180
You old lady.

31:40.210 --> 31:41.580
Qiao Qingyu, say something.

31:41.580 --> 31:43.050
You seem to be pretty covered up.

31:43.250 --> 31:44.110
Are you trying to avoid
being recognized?

31:44.110 --> 31:44.480
Yeah.

31:44.510 --> 31:46.210
I think maybe she's a human trafficker.

31:46.250 --> 31:47.250
I'm not.

31:47.250 --> 31:48.150
Qiao Qingyu!

31:48.250 --> 31:49.680
She's ignoring you.

31:50.050 --> 31:50.750
What are you doing?

31:51.380 --> 31:52.080
Qingyu!

31:53.510 --> 31:54.580
Explain yourself.

31:56.180 --> 31:57.850
She's ignoring you.

31:57.850 --> 31:58.580
Don't get physical.

31:58.610 --> 32:01.410
Explain first.

32:02.050 --> 32:03.510
Explain yourself.

32:03.510 --> 32:04.510
Qiao Qingyu!

32:24.250 --> 32:24.910
Qiao Qingyu.

32:29.850 --> 32:30.610
What do you want?

32:33.510 --> 32:34.210
Answer me.

32:36.410 --> 32:37.310
What do you want?

32:38.880 --> 32:40.180
Do you think you'll be free

32:40.210 --> 32:41.080
after the police take me away?

32:41.080 --> 32:41.410
Enough.

32:41.450 --> 32:42.080
Speak up!

32:42.080 --> 32:42.710
Alright.

32:42.910 --> 32:44.210
She knows she's wrong.

32:44.480 --> 32:45.750
Apologize to your mom.

32:45.750 --> 32:46.780
Just say you won't do it again.

32:46.810 --> 32:48.180
Why should I apologize?

32:48.810 --> 32:49.810
Qiao Qingyu, remember this.

32:50.210 --> 32:51.710
My responsibility for you
lasts a lifetime.

32:51.810 --> 32:52.750
I'm your mother.

32:52.810 --> 32:53.750
Alright.

32:54.180 --> 32:55.280
The knife is over there.

32:55.310 --> 32:56.310
Kill me if you dare.

32:56.450 --> 32:58.150
Then you'll be free

32:58.180 --> 32:58.410
of me.

32:58.410 --> 32:59.850
You disrespected me first.

33:00.510 --> 33:00.980
Why did you...?

33:02.750 --> 33:03.450
Qiao Qingyu.

33:03.450 --> 33:04.280
Calm down. Don't hit her.

33:04.310 --> 33:05.880
We sacrificed so much
for your upbringing

33:05.950 --> 33:06.750
and education.

33:06.750 --> 33:07.050
Get out.

33:07.050 --> 33:08.110
Don't come back if you dare!

33:08.980 --> 33:10.110
I disrespected you?

33:10.150 --> 33:11.550
Enough.

33:11.550 --> 33:12.550
She'll turn on you

33:12.550 --> 33:13.450
just like she did me.

33:13.450 --> 33:15.450
You could have talked it out.
Why hit her?

33:15.450 --> 33:16.380
You always take her side!

33:18.250 --> 33:19.080
Oh, you...

33:19.680 --> 33:21.110
She's right.

33:22.150 --> 33:22.880
Well...

33:22.950 --> 33:24.750
You need to respect her opinion too.

33:24.880 --> 33:26.050
Besides, she's already grown up.

33:26.250 --> 33:27.550
Try not to worry so much.

33:28.410 --> 33:29.080
Qiao Lusheng.

33:29.510 --> 33:30.610
How often

33:31.250 --> 33:32.110
have you actually disciplined her?

33:33.250 --> 33:34.580
Have you ever acted like a father?

33:38.310 --> 33:39.580
You don't care

33:39.850 --> 33:41.350
or get involved,

33:41.380 --> 33:42.450
so I have to worry about everything.

33:48.650 --> 33:49.580
Beiyu...

33:49.610 --> 33:51.010
Beiyu wasn't with me,

33:51.550 --> 33:53.250
and her grandparents failed
to raise her properly.

33:53.450 --> 33:54.850
Every time I saw her,

33:57.050 --> 33:58.950
I couldn't bear to discipline her.
And look what happened.

34:01.980 --> 34:03.850
I can't watch Qingyu

34:03.850 --> 34:05.080
end up like that too.

34:14.350 --> 34:15.610
We were talking about our children.

34:15.610 --> 34:17.310
Why did you bring up my parents?

34:19.010 --> 34:20.510
Besides,
it's not like they ignored Beiyu.

34:20.550 --> 34:22.150
Didn't they also work hard

34:22.179 --> 34:23.550
raising Beiyu?

34:26.610 --> 34:27.480
Qiao Lusheng.

34:28.580 --> 34:31.679
I never asked them to raise my daughter.

34:34.350 --> 34:36.580
They took her away from me,

34:36.880 --> 34:38.380
and you let them!

34:42.050 --> 34:44.310
All for your vanity

34:44.310 --> 34:45.510
and face!

34:45.909 --> 34:47.810
I shouldn't have listened to you.

34:49.380 --> 34:52.510
I should have run away with Beiyu.

35:11.580 --> 35:12.410
Here.

35:14.910 --> 35:15.750
Take it.

35:21.210 --> 35:24.780
There's nothing wrong
with changing your name.

35:25.950 --> 35:28.380
I think you should take this opportunity

35:28.650 --> 35:31.010
to change to a better name.

35:31.480 --> 35:32.980
How about I change it with you?

35:33.150 --> 35:34.780
Let's get matching names.

35:34.950 --> 35:36.010
This way,

35:36.010 --> 35:37.250
others will know that we are siblings.

35:55.280 --> 35:56.380
Everyone.

35:56.410 --> 35:57.580
Some of you missed

35:57.610 --> 35:59.910
yesterday's school seminar

35:59.910 --> 36:01.650
on preventing campus bullying

36:01.680 --> 36:03.710
and protecting students.

36:03.710 --> 36:05.210
I have had their names recorded.

36:05.250 --> 36:07.280
Come over to explain after this.

36:07.280 --> 36:07.980
Well,

36:08.010 --> 36:09.450
Monitor, hand out
the winter break homework

36:09.450 --> 36:10.280
and report cards later.

36:10.780 --> 36:11.880
I'll stop nagging.

36:12.080 --> 36:13.510
Complete your homework on time

36:13.780 --> 36:15.480
and be careful when you play outside.

36:15.850 --> 36:18.280
I wish you all a happy winter break.

37:18.010 --> 37:19.510
Is it already winter break?

37:20.710 --> 37:21.910
Sorry.

37:22.450 --> 37:24.450
My asking around for Hei

37:24.580 --> 37:25.750
led to him finding you.

37:27.010 --> 37:28.080
It has nothing to do with you.

37:28.250 --> 37:29.580
I was looking for him myself.

37:30.080 --> 37:31.480
Besides, it's over.

37:31.750 --> 37:33.610
Is he the one you're looking for?

37:43.210 --> 37:44.810
After Beiyu dropped out,

37:44.950 --> 37:47.350
your parents came to help her pack,

37:47.650 --> 37:49.280
but despite searching thoroughly,

37:50.310 --> 37:51.580
they couldn't find

37:51.780 --> 37:52.910
what she'd hidden.

37:53.710 --> 37:54.480
I think

37:54.750 --> 37:57.280
it might contain the clue you need.

38:30.010 --> 38:32.480
The country is experiencing
its worst cold wave in a century.

38:32.480 --> 38:33.910
Since mid-last month,

38:33.950 --> 38:34.680
heavy snow has blanketed

38:34.680 --> 38:36.250
central and eastern China's
mountainous regions,

38:36.950 --> 38:38.480
leading to the closure

38:38.750 --> 38:40.950
of many expressways in our province

38:41.180 --> 38:43.210
and severe transportation disruptions.

38:43.710 --> 38:44.480
Experts predict

38:44.480 --> 38:47.280
this will continue
until Chinese New Year.

39:01.480 --> 39:03.710
Qingyu, Mom wants you to have this.

39:10.780 --> 39:14.980
Mom, I don't feel like eating either.

39:35.210 --> 39:36.280
There's something wrong with the bus.

39:36.310 --> 39:37.410
I'll get off to check it out.

39:38.250 --> 39:39.710
Sir, can you fix it?

39:40.080 --> 39:41.850
Hold on, I'll go see what's wrong.

39:50.050 --> 39:52.080
The bus is broken down,
and repairs will take an hour or so.

39:52.080 --> 39:53.250
We're about five kilometers away.

39:53.250 --> 39:54.410
Anyone who's in a hurry
can get off here.

39:54.750 --> 39:56.350
Sir, could we get our money back?

39:56.480 --> 39:56.980
No.

40:03.710 --> 40:04.880
What if it can't be fixed?

40:07.410 --> 40:08.080
Didn't he say

40:08.080 --> 40:09.480
it will be fixed in an hour or so?

40:10.050 --> 40:11.750
It's about five kilometers from here.

40:12.010 --> 40:13.050
How long will it take to walk?

40:14.010 --> 40:14.710
It's freezing.

40:15.780 --> 40:17.180
We also have so much stuff.

40:31.550 --> 40:33.450
Mom, how about you give me

40:33.450 --> 40:34.450
the tea egg?

40:35.080 --> 40:36.380
I'm a little hungry.

40:47.350 --> 40:48.410
Save one for your sister.

40:50.310 --> 40:51.150
She doesn't want it.

40:57.080 --> 40:58.680
Dad, Mom.

40:59.180 --> 40:59.880
We're back.

40:59.880 --> 41:00.250
Dad.

41:00.380 --> 41:00.680
Oh.

41:00.710 --> 41:03.710
Lusheng, you're back.
I was worried sick.

41:03.950 --> 41:05.550
The bus broke down on the road

41:05.550 --> 41:06.480
and delayed us for a while.

41:08.080 --> 41:09.310
You must be freezing, Yu.

41:09.810 --> 41:11.250
Is the ginger soup ready?

41:11.480 --> 41:12.350
It's ready.

41:13.010 --> 41:13.680
I bought this for you.

41:13.710 --> 41:14.980
- Hurry.
- Put it on the table.

41:14.980 --> 41:15.880
The ginger soup is here.

41:16.210 --> 41:16.950
You're all back.

41:16.980 --> 41:18.480
I'll turn in for the night.

41:18.480 --> 41:19.950
Alright, go get some rest.

41:19.980 --> 41:22.010
- I'm freezing.
- Here. Hurry.

41:22.050 --> 41:22.980
Have some ginger soup.

41:23.550 --> 41:24.850
- Here.
- Take it.

41:24.850 --> 41:25.710
Mom, let me do it.

41:26.010 --> 41:27.410
Here, hurry.

41:27.650 --> 41:28.310
Yanfen,

41:28.980 --> 41:30.650
how is Jinrui's marriage going?

41:31.010 --> 41:32.450
They've got the certificate.

41:33.980 --> 41:34.780
Great.

41:34.780 --> 41:35.450
Thank you, Grandma.

41:35.610 --> 41:37.280
Grandma, I'm freezing too.

41:37.610 --> 41:38.680
Can't you get it yourself?

41:39.410 --> 41:40.480
My daughter-in-law can't run away now.

41:41.480 --> 41:42.710
She is

41:42.950 --> 41:45.610
beautiful and well-educated.

41:45.850 --> 41:47.250
She's also an only child.

41:47.850 --> 41:50.450
She can help Jinrui in the future.

41:51.380 --> 41:52.010
By the way,

41:52.080 --> 41:54.750
they city people don't do
the whole betrothal gift thing.

41:56.080 --> 41:57.650
Everything's good.

41:57.780 --> 41:58.250
Good.

41:58.250 --> 41:59.950
We're lucky

42:00.380 --> 42:02.780
that Jinrui gets to marry Xiaoyun.

42:03.010 --> 42:03.810
Great.

42:04.080 --> 42:06.550
You're making it sound like
we're marrying up.

42:06.880 --> 42:10.250
My grandson is
our county's top scorer in NCEE.

42:10.850 --> 42:11.950
Not just Xiaoyun,

42:12.350 --> 42:13.480
we're good enough

42:13.750 --> 42:15.010
for plenty of women like her.

42:16.150 --> 42:16.880
Yes.

42:17.850 --> 42:21.450
A couple of days ago, the secretary
added Jinrui and Xiaoyun's names

42:21.750 --> 42:23.010
to the genealogy book.

42:23.380 --> 42:24.380
Now,

42:24.610 --> 42:26.710
it's up to Jinrui

42:26.750 --> 42:29.410
to uphold the Qiao family's reputation.

42:30.210 --> 42:30.810
Grandma.

42:31.150 --> 42:33.510
When will Qingyu's and my names
be entered into the genealogy?

42:34.310 --> 42:35.850
When you get married,

42:36.210 --> 42:38.380
we'll ask the secretary to add yours.

42:39.310 --> 42:40.350
What about Qingyu?

42:40.880 --> 42:42.110
Qing's a girl.

42:42.580 --> 42:44.210
She'll get married someday.

42:44.710 --> 42:45.310
Yes.

42:46.880 --> 42:48.310
I'll put the luggage upstairs.

42:49.080 --> 42:49.380
Okay.

42:50.210 --> 42:51.510
Go get unpacked.

42:53.150 --> 42:54.350
Lusheng, sit down.

42:54.580 --> 42:55.050
Okay.

42:55.050 --> 42:55.350
Sit down.

42:55.380 --> 42:55.980
You too, Aunt Yanfen.

42:56.150 --> 42:56.410
Okay.

42:56.410 --> 42:57.280
I'll have more, Grandma.

42:57.950 --> 42:59.580
Yu, eat up.

43:00.610 --> 43:02.150
I'm good. You guys go ahead.

43:35.910 --> 43:39.580
ظآزPerhapsظآز

43:40.110 --> 43:45.810
ظآزThe more we care,
the more careful we becomeظآز

43:46.950 --> 43:52.350
ظآزCounting the distance
that separates usظآز

43:53.350 --> 43:58.880
ظآزA single step,
and we'd be closer stillظآز

44:04.580 --> 44:08.250
ظآزIn the futureظآز

44:08.710 --> 44:14.410
ظآزTime will reveal this secretظآز

44:15.950 --> 44:21.010
ظآزWaiting is a silent promiseظآز

44:22.250 --> 44:27.380
ظآزThat never expiresظآز

44:31.010 --> 44:35.480
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

44:36.480 --> 44:40.150
ظآزIs your nameظآز

44:40.650 --> 44:45.750
ظآزThe only stubbornness in my heartظآز

44:46.850 --> 44:50.050
ظآزAt first sightظآز

44:50.480 --> 44:53.750
ظآزThe future has been determinedظآز

44:54.450 --> 44:59.980
ظآزDreams began to feel realظآز

45:01.110 --> 45:04.650
ظآزTurns out that what's on your mindظآز

45:05.110 --> 45:09.050
ظآزIs a placeظآز

45:09.350 --> 45:14.880
ظآزWhere the same story is held dearظآز

45:15.580 --> 45:18.950
ظآزFortunately, I'm not sensible enoughظآز

45:19.280 --> 45:22.750
ظآزCourage wasn't late tooظآز

45:23.280 --> 45:29.350
ظآزOnly then does time not betray
our acquaintanceظآز
